1
00:00:51,359 --> 00:00:52,920
I'll use your identity

2
00:00:54,359 --> 00:00:56,200
to pay back the insults to my family

3
00:00:56,479 --> 00:00:58,679
a hundredfold.

4
00:01:18,959 --> 00:01:21,239
Just use this Key of Fate,

5
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:24,599
go to the home of someone

6
00:01:24,599 --> 00:01:25,680
of the same sex and age as you,

7
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:27,560
and eat a meal there.

8
00:01:28,280 --> 00:01:30,000
Then you will Exchange Lives

9
00:01:30,439 --> 00:01:31,439
with him.

10
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:33,799
His wealth,

11
00:01:34,280 --> 00:01:35,040
his power,

12
00:01:35,519 --> 00:01:37,599
and his parents and lover

13
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:39,599
will all become yours.

14
00:01:49,159 --> 00:01:49,760
Let go!

15
00:01:55,959 --> 00:01:56,359
I'm sorry.

16
00:02:00,239 --> 00:02:00,920
Sheng Yuanzhou!

17
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:03,480
What did you do to Zhang Xiaobei?

18
00:02:04,239 --> 00:02:05,519
Sheng Yuanzhou!

19
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:18,319
I really did Exchange Lives with him.

20
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:44,520
Zhang Xiaobei.

21
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,240
Your Sis getting photographed like that

22
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:47,280
only proves she's stupid.

23
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,879
If she wanted to go from rags to riches,

24
00:02:49,879 --> 00:02:51,039
she had to pay the price.

25
00:02:51,039 --> 00:02:52,159
Sheng Yuanzhou!

26
00:02:53,199 --> 00:02:54,960
You dared to bully my Sis!

27
00:02:55,159 --> 00:02:56,240
I won't let you get away with this!

28
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:04,319
The moment she took off her clothes,

29
00:03:04,319 --> 00:03:05,240
she should've known

30
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:08,680
she was nothing but a plaything.

31
00:03:13,919 --> 00:03:14,759
I'm warning you.

32
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:16,280
Be smart.

33
00:03:16,759 --> 00:03:18,240
Drop this whole thing about your Sis.

34
00:03:18,639 --> 00:03:19,599
Don't ask for trouble.

35
00:03:25,599 --> 00:03:26,479
Throw him out!

36
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:49,759
Is there any justice left in this world?

37
00:03:50,639 --> 00:03:51,800
You've gone too far!

38
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,279
Let's go, Sis.

39
00:04:38,439 --> 00:04:38,920
Xiaobei.

40
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:40,879
This is a gift for you.

41
00:04:42,199 --> 00:04:42,720
Sis...

42
00:04:43,279 --> 00:04:44,480
I've already found a new job.

43
00:04:44,839 --> 00:04:45,959
Try it on, hurry.

44
00:04:45,959 --> 00:04:46,519
I...

45
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:48,319
Okay, okay, okay.

46
00:04:49,279 --> 00:04:49,959
Thanks, Sis.

47
00:04:50,959 --> 00:04:52,079
My new job is being a secretary

48
00:04:52,279 --> 00:04:54,800
for your classmate Sheng Yuanzhou.

49
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:57,279
Not bad, right?

50
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:58,920
His family runs a huge corporation.

51
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:00,120
Sis!

52
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:01,519
Sis!

53
00:05:08,399 --> 00:05:09,399
Sheng Yuanzhou!

54
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:11,879
I won't let you get away with this!

55
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:19,319
Honey!

56
00:05:19,319 --> 00:05:20,279
Xiaobei! Xiaobei!

57
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:20,959
Mom!

58
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:22,360
Mom!

59
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:23,199
Honey!

60
00:05:23,639 --> 00:05:24,120
Mom!

61
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:25,639
Mom!

62
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:31,040
The patient is in critical condition now.

63
00:05:31,199 --> 00:05:32,759
Anything could happen at any moment.

64
00:05:32,959 --> 00:05:33,519
She needs surgery immediately.

65
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,560
How much will the surgery cost?

66
00:05:35,759 --> 00:05:36,639
About 100,000 yuan.

67
00:05:38,279 --> 00:05:39,240
100,000...

68
00:05:43,759 --> 00:05:44,480
Where are you going?

69
00:05:45,399 --> 00:05:47,079
To raise money for your mom.

70
00:05:49,079 --> 00:05:50,800
Where are you going to get the money?

71
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:51,240
I...

72
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:53,639
I'll sell my blood, my kidney.

73
00:05:53,839 --> 00:05:54,839
There has to be a way to get the money.

74
00:05:55,279 --> 00:05:56,639
Even if it costs me my life,

75
00:05:56,759 --> 00:05:57,720
I have to save your mom.

76
00:05:58,160 --> 00:05:58,680
Dad...

77
00:05:59,519 --> 00:06:00,319
I'm begging you.

78
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:02,279
Please stop making things worse for us.

79
00:06:03,399 --> 00:06:04,839
If you hadn't played the futures market,

80
00:06:04,839 --> 00:06:05,399
and opened a restaurant,

81
00:06:05,639 --> 00:06:07,199
would our family be in this mess?

82
00:06:07,399 --> 00:06:08,319
I can't just

83
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:12,000
stand by and watch your mom die!

84
00:06:14,199 --> 00:06:14,680
Sir...

85
00:06:15,199 --> 00:06:15,600
Xiaobei.

86
00:06:16,199 --> 00:06:16,839
I have money.

87
00:06:28,199 --> 00:06:30,000
Dad, why won't my credit card work?

88
00:06:30,399 --> 00:06:31,079
I froze it.

89
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:32,639
I thought you had a spine.

90
00:06:33,160 --> 00:06:33,839
I set you up with

91
00:06:33,839 --> 00:06:35,240
such a great marriage with the Shengs,

92
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:37,680
and you dared reject them to their face.

93
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:39,800
You insisted on being with that poor boy,

94
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:42,160
and wanted to use my money to feed trash.

95
00:06:42,639 --> 00:06:43,079
Not a chance.

96
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:44,120
Without money,

97
00:06:44,519 --> 00:06:46,560
you'll come crawling back sooner or later.

98
00:06:47,879 --> 00:06:48,720
Dad, I...

99
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:55,680
I'm sorry.

100
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:58,519
Don't apologize.

101
00:06:58,920 --> 00:06:59,920
You were helping me in the first place.

102
00:07:00,639 --> 00:07:01,560
About the surgery fee,

103
00:07:02,639 --> 00:07:03,639
don't worry about it anymore.

104
00:07:05,959 --> 00:07:06,680
Don't forget,

105
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:07,519
I still have

106
00:07:08,199 --> 00:07:10,279
an AI project that's almost finished.

107
00:07:10,279 --> 00:07:11,399
A lot of companies

108
00:07:11,399 --> 00:07:12,600
are already discussing investments with me.

109
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:14,639
I'll earn the money soon.

110
00:07:36,279 --> 00:07:37,040
Where were you?

111
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:39,319
I...

112
00:07:41,879 --> 00:07:44,240
I went to an employee's funeral.

113
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:46,079
Why would you go to a place like that?

114
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:48,279
I...

115
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:52,800
To deliver the condolence payment.

116
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:55,480
She was a company employee, after all.

117
00:08:21,079 --> 00:08:21,720
I was wrong.

118
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:26,839
Where did you go wrong?

119
00:08:27,639 --> 00:08:28,279
I...

120
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:30,199
I mishandled Zhang Xiaoyu's situation.

121
00:08:30,199 --> 00:08:30,600
Wrong.

122
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:33,919
You were wrong to be afraid.

123
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:34,759
Cowering and hesitating...

124
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,799
How will you ever achieve great things?

125
00:08:37,159 --> 00:08:39,000
If someone like her dies, so what?

126
00:08:39,679 --> 00:08:41,440
That worthless life isn't worth a thing.

127
00:08:41,679 --> 00:08:42,840
Don't waste your energy

128
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:44,600
on a worthless life like that.

129
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,799
Put away your useless sympathy.

130
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:48,279
Do what you're supposed to do.

131
00:08:50,799 --> 00:08:51,480
Yes.

132
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:53,559
Get up.

133
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:58,519
The AI project you provided recently

134
00:08:58,519 --> 00:08:59,240
is quite impressive.

135
00:08:59,799 --> 00:09:00,679
Did you develop it?

136
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:02,000
No.

137
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:03,600
No, I didn't.

138
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:08,919
Whether you developed it or not,

139
00:09:09,519 --> 00:09:10,799
claim it as your own.

140
00:09:11,720 --> 00:09:12,240
Do you understand?

141
00:09:13,039 --> 00:09:13,559
I understand.

142
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:16,840
Keep up the good work.

143
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:18,679
You are my son, after all.

144
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:56,720
Hello, Mr. Han.

145
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:59,480
Let me explain it to you in detail again.

146
00:10:01,519 --> 00:10:03,000
Hello, I'm Zhang Xiaobei.

147
00:10:03,519 --> 00:10:05,279
That project I told you about last time...

148
00:10:06,679 --> 00:10:07,120
Hello?

149
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:09,759
Mr. Xu, didn't you say last time

150
00:10:09,759 --> 00:10:11,240
about the AI project I developed,

151
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:12,000
that you were really interested?

152
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:12,840
We...

153
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:13,720
To be honest with you,

154
00:10:14,279 --> 00:10:15,200
it's not that I'm not interested,

155
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:17,399
I just don't dare to be.

156
00:10:17,879 --> 00:10:19,879
Prosperity Group's Young Master spoke.

157
00:10:20,279 --> 00:10:21,879
He's taking your project, no matter what.

158
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:23,600
If anyone dares invest in your project,

159
00:10:23,919 --> 00:10:25,159
they're going against the Sheng family.

160
00:10:26,039 --> 00:10:26,600
Now,

161
00:10:26,919 --> 00:10:28,360
no one dares touch your project anymore.

162
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:30,679
Prosperity Group, Sheng Yuanzhou.

163
00:10:31,679 --> 00:10:33,440
So please don't make things hard for me.

164
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:41,240
As a young entrepreneur,

165
00:10:41,679 --> 00:10:43,000
I've always put people first

166
00:10:43,559 --> 00:10:44,600
and actively given back to society.

167
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:46,399
We have created many jobs

168
00:10:46,399 --> 00:10:47,799
for this city.

169
00:10:48,399 --> 00:10:49,000
I hope

170
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:51,559
we can live up to our group's name

171
00:10:52,039 --> 00:10:54,279
and bring this city lasting prosperity.

172
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:14,840
Some people are born

173
00:11:15,639 --> 00:11:17,000
with the wind at their back,

174
00:11:17,639 --> 00:11:18,919
getting whatever they wish for,

175
00:11:19,679 --> 00:11:21,320
and having everything they could want.

176
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:24,200
But others

177
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:26,799
struggle like hell

178
00:11:27,360 --> 00:11:29,000
and end up with nothing.

179
00:11:34,679 --> 00:11:35,320
Ma'am.

180
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:37,080
I don't have any money.

181
00:11:38,360 --> 00:11:39,159
I've only got food.

182
00:11:39,879 --> 00:11:40,759
Here, you can have this to eat.

183
00:11:41,559 --> 00:11:42,360
If you want money,

184
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:43,159
go ask someone else.

185
00:11:43,759 --> 00:11:44,679
Young man.

186
00:11:46,759 --> 00:11:48,519
If I gave you

187
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:51,559
a chance to Exchange Lives with someone,

188
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:53,159
would you take it?

189
00:11:56,759 --> 00:11:57,480
Exchange Lives?

190
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:13,039
Just use this Key of Fate,

191
00:12:13,399 --> 00:12:15,320
go to the home of someone

192
00:12:15,320 --> 00:12:17,519
of the same sex and age as you,

193
00:12:17,840 --> 00:12:21,240
and eat a meal with this Key of Fate.

194
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:24,399
and you will Exchange Lives with him.

195
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:27,879
His wealth and power,

196
00:12:28,399 --> 00:12:30,399
and his parents and lover

197
00:12:30,960 --> 00:12:33,120
will all become yours.

198
00:12:50,159 --> 00:12:51,559
Young Master Sheng, it's our fault.

199
00:12:51,559 --> 00:12:52,679
We'll drag him out right now.

200
00:12:54,360 --> 00:12:55,679
Where'd this filthy beggar come from?

201
00:12:55,919 --> 00:12:56,679
Get the hell out, now!

202
00:12:57,120 --> 00:12:58,600
Don't ruin Young Master Sheng's fun.

203
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:00,200
Watch your mouth.

204
00:13:00,639 --> 00:13:02,159
He's my college classmate.

205
00:13:02,639 --> 00:13:04,039
He's a true man of talent.

206
00:13:05,080 --> 00:13:07,519
Only Young Master Sheng is a man of wealth.

207
00:13:09,679 --> 00:13:10,879
You're such a money-grubber.

208
00:13:13,840 --> 00:13:14,679
You filthy beggar,

209
00:13:14,679 --> 00:13:15,799
how dare you snatch food?

210
00:13:28,080 --> 00:13:30,600
Mr. Zhang, what took you so long?

211
00:13:30,600 --> 00:13:31,559
We've been waiting forever.

212
00:13:31,840 --> 00:13:32,559
Mr. Zhang,

213
00:13:32,919 --> 00:13:33,960
your outfit today

214
00:13:34,399 --> 00:13:35,440
is so... unique.

215
00:13:36,559 --> 00:13:39,159
Is that this year's trendy distressed look?

216
00:13:40,440 --> 00:13:41,120
Who are you?

217
00:13:41,279 --> 00:13:42,360
Why are you sitting in Mr. Zhang's seat?

218
00:13:42,360 --> 00:13:43,159
Get the hell out, now!

219
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:44,200
You got the seat all dirty.

220
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:48,519
Sorry, I... I didn't mean to.

221
00:13:50,240 --> 00:13:50,799
I'm sorry.

222
00:13:51,759 --> 00:13:53,559
Sheng Yuanzhou, look at you now.

223
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:56,279
This one. Here.

224
00:13:57,320 --> 00:13:57,759
Okay.

